ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend it to another student.
I would recommend it to a fellow student, but I would advise him/her tonot take the course until he/she is ready to submit a career development award, ideally for the June submission date.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course was helpful in understanding the fundamentals of grant writing. Although the course is helpful for my career, it was not specifically helpful for my dissertation or research.
